de.iabg.swing
Class KeyList

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.AbstractListModel
      de.iabg.swing.KeyList
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.ComboBoxModel, javax.swing.ListModel
public class KeyList
extends javax.swing.AbstractListModel
implements javax.swing.ComboBoxModel

This ComboBoxModel is backed by an ArrayList since there are several instances where it is convenient to have this combination. The methods in this class simply wrap those in ArrayList or they use the list to implement the methods declared in ComboBoxModel.

Version:
September 10, 2008
Author:
